data.text:
Being there for every foster child takes hard work, determination and collaboration. We are extremely grateful for the support we receive from our government, foundation, corporate and community partners. Their compassion and generosity enables us to LIFT UP our foster children. This list reflects our donors in calendar year 2022. Join them to STAND UP for foster kids by contacting development@childadvocatessv.org.
